OUTAGES AND EMERGENCIES


Report outages onlineReport an outageCheck outage status Report outages by phone1-877-PEPCO-62 (1-877-737-2662) Report downed wires and life-threatening emergencies by phone1-877-PEPCO-62 (1-877-737-2662) and follow the promptsTTY: 202-872-2369We regret that we cannot respond to outages reported by email. Please do not dial 911 for outage information or to report power outages.




CUSTOMER SERVICE


Contact Customer Care by phoneAvailable 7 a.m. - 8 p.m. Monday through Friday202-833-7500Servicio en Espanol: 202-872-4641




CALL BEFORE YOU DIG


By law, you must call at least 48 hours before any digging or construction.Contact Miss Utility or District One by phoneDial 811Visit Miss Utility's website for more information.




BILLING QUESTIONS


Contact Customer Care by phone202-833-7500Learn how to read your bill.




