Potomac Electric Power Co Government Contractor in Washington, DC

 






dollars obligated (Latest year)$405,824 United States dollarslatest fiscal year2016total dollars obligated (Since FY2007)$35,544,974 United States dollarsnumber of contracts (Since FY2007)13 

 

