Advertisement


ShareOverviewSummaryPotomac Electric Power Co has worked on thirteen contracts worth $35.5 million USD in obligations from the federal government since FY2007. In its latest active fiscal year (2016), the organization received a total of $405,824 USD in obligations.The principal agencies it has contracted with are the General Services Administration and Office of Personnel Management.

Principal Agencies
General Services AdministrationOffice of Personnel Management


Principal Category (NAICS)
Electric Power Distribution (221122)


Principal Product or Service (PSC)
Electric Services (S112)


Designations
Other than Small Business
 





